#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag6.7:4.1"
msgid "6.7. Kātiyānattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc411"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts411"></a>
msgctxt "thag6.7:5.1"
msgid "“Uṭṭhehi nisīda kātiyāna,"
msgstr "Get up, Kātiyāna, and sit!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:5.2"
msgid "Mā niddābahulo ahu jāgarassu;"
msgstr "Don’t sleep too much, be wakeful."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:5.3"
msgid "Mā taṃ alasaṃ pamattabandhu,"
msgstr "Don’t be lazy, and let the kinsman of the heedless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:5.4"
msgid "Kūṭeneva jinātu maccurājā."
msgstr "The king of death, catch you in his trap."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc412"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts412"></a>
msgctxt "thag6.7:6.1"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"sayathāpi (bj, pts1-2)\" id=\"note216\">Seyyathāpi</span> mahāsamuddavego,"
msgstr "Like a wave in the mighty ocean,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:6.2"
msgid "Evaṃ jātijarātivattate taṃ;"
msgstr "Birth and old age overwhelm you."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:6.3"
msgid "So karohi sudīpamattano tvaṃ,"
msgstr "Make a safe island of yourself,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:6.4"
msgid "Na hi tāṇaṃ tava vijjateva aññaṃ."
msgstr "For you have no other shelter."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc413"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts413"></a>
msgctxt "thag6.7:7.1"
msgid "Satthā hi vijesi maggametaṃ,"
msgstr "The teacher has mastered this path,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:7.2"
msgid "Saṅgā jātijarābhayā atītaṃ;"
msgstr "Which transcends ties, and the fear of birth and old age."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:7.3"
msgid "Pubbāpararattamappamatto,"
msgstr "Be heedful all the time,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:7.4"
msgid "Anuyuñjassu daḷhaṃ karohi yogaṃ."
msgstr "And devote yourself to dedicated practice."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc414"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts414"></a>
msgctxt "thag6.7:8.1"
msgid "Purimāni pamuñca bandhanāni,"
msgstr "Be free of your former bonds!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:8.2"
msgid "Saṅghāṭikhuramuṇḍabhikkhabhojī;"
msgstr "Wearing outer robe, with shaven head, eating almsfood,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:8.3"
msgid "Mā khiḍḍāratiñca mā niddaṃ,"
msgstr "Don’t delight in play or sleep,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:8.4"
msgid "Anuyuñjittha jhāya kātiyāna."
msgstr "Devote yourself to jhāna, Kātiyāna."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc415"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts415"></a><a class="pts" id="pts45"></a>
msgctxt "thag6.7:9.1"
msgid "Jhāyāhi jināhi kātiyāna,"
msgstr "Practice jhāna and conquer, Kātiyāna,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:9.2"
msgid "Yogakkhemapathesu <span class=\"var\" title=\"... pathe sukovidosi (s2, s3, pts1)\" id=\"note217\">kovidosi</span>;"
msgstr "You’re skilled in the path to security from the yoke."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:9.3"
msgid "Pappuyya anuttaraṃ visuddhiṃ,"
msgstr "Attaining unexcelled purity,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:9.4"
msgid "Parinibbāhisi vārināva joti."
msgstr "You’ll be quenched, like a flame by water."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc416"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts416"></a>
msgctxt "thag6.7:10.1"
msgid "Pajjotakaro parittaraṃso,"
msgstr "A lamp with feeble flames"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:10.2"
msgid "Vātena vinamyate latāva;"
msgstr "Is bent down by the wind, like a creeper;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:10.3"
msgid "Evampi tuvaṃ anādiyāno,"
msgstr "Just so, kinsman of Indra,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:10.4"
msgid "Māraṃ indasagotta niddhunāhi;"
msgstr "You shake off Māra, without grasping."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:10.5"
msgid "So vedayitāsu vītarāgo,"
msgstr "Free of lust for feelings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag6.7:10.6"
msgid "Kālaṃ kaṅkha idheva sītibhūto”ti."
msgstr "Await your time here, cooled."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
